{"parentUuid":null,"isSidechain":true,"promptId":"1aafe049-f829-4ef0-bb04-865aac195e09","agentId":"a999acd45dac71e5c","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":"You are implementing Task 17 of an auth implementation plan for a NestJS + Fastify backend.\n\n## Context\n- Working directory: /Users/4thwithme/Documents/repo/no-name-proj/backend\n- NestJS 11 + Fastify, strict TypeScript\n- Read backend/CLAUDE.md for conventions\n- Tabs for indentation (useTabs: true), printWidth: 90\n\n## Files to READ first:\n- src/modules/app/app.module.ts — current root module\n- src/modules/auth/ — all auth files created so far\n- src/modules/env-config/env-config.module.ts\n- src/constants/env-variables.constant.ts — JWT_SECRET, JWT_ACCESS_TOKEN_EXPIRY\n\n## Convention Rules (CRITICAL)\n- NO comments in code\n- NO relative imports — use @aliases only\n- ALL functions must have explicit return types\n\n## Task: Create Auth Module + Update App Module\n\n### Step 1: Create AuthModule\n\nFile: `src/modules/auth/auth.module.ts`\n\n```typescript\nimport { Module } from '@nestjs/common';\nimport { JwtModule } from '@nestjs/jwt';\n\n// Import all auth components\nimport { AuthController } from '@modules/auth/auth.controller';\nimport { AuthService } from '@modules/auth/auth.service';\nimport { AuthGuard } from '@modules/auth/guards/auth.guard';\nimport { RolesGuard } from '@modules/auth/guards/roles.guard';\nimport { GithubStrategy } from '@modules/auth/strategies/github.strategy';\nimport { GoogleStrategy } from '@modules/auth/strategies/google.strategy';\n\n// Import dependent modules\nimport { CompanyMemberModule } from '@modules/company-member/company-member.module';\nimport { CompanyModule } from '@modules/company/company.module';\nimport { EnvConfigModule } from '@modules/env-config/env-config.module';\nimport { EnvConfigService } from '@modules/env-config/env-config.service';\nimport { OAuthAccountModule } from '@modules/oauth-account/oauth-account.module';\nimport { SessionModule } from '@modules/session/session.module';\nimport { UserModule } from '@modules/user/user.module';\n\nimport { JWT_ACCESS_TOKEN_EXPIRY, JWT_SECRET } from '@constants/env-variables.constant';\n\n@Module({\n  imports: [\n    JwtModule.registerAsync({\n      imports: [EnvConfigModule],\n      inject: [EnvConfigService],\n      useFactory: (envConfig: EnvConfigService) => ({\n        secret: envConfig.get<string>({ key: JWT_SECRET }),\n        signOptions: {\n          expiresIn: envConfig.get<number>({\n            key: JWT_ACCESS_TOKEN_EXPIRY,\n            converter: Number,\n          }),\n        },\n      }),\n    }),\n    UserModule,\n    OAuthAccountModule,\n    CompanyModule,\n    CompanyMemberModule,\n    SessionModule,\n    EnvConfigModule,\n  ],\n  controllers: [AuthController],\n  providers: [AuthService, GithubStrategy, GoogleStrategy, AuthGuard, RolesGuard],\n  exports: [AuthGuard, RolesGuard, JwtModule],\n})\nexport class AuthModule {}\n```\n\n### Step 2: Update AppModule\n\nFile: `src/modules/app/app.module.ts`\n\nRead the current file first. Then update to:\n\n```typescript\nimport { Module } from '@nestjs/common';\nimport { APP_GUARD } from '@nestjs/core';\nimport { ThrottlerModule } from '@nestjs/throttler';\n\nimport { AuthGuard } from '@modules/auth/guards/auth.guard';\nimport { FastifyThrottlerGuard } from '@modules/auth/guards/fastify-throttler.guard';\nimport { RolesGuard } from '@modules/auth/guards/roles.guard';\n\nimport { AuthModule } from '@modules/auth/auth.module';\nimport { CacheModule } from '@modules/cache/cache.module';\nimport { CompanyMemberModule } from '@modules/company-member/company-member.module';\nimport { CompanyModule } from '@modules/company/company.module';\nimport { DbModule } from '@modules/db/db.module';\nimport { EnvConfigModule } from '@modules/env-config/env-config.module';\nimport { HealthModule } from '@modules/health/health.module';\nimport { SessionModule } from '@modules/session/session.module';\nimport { UserModule } from '@modules/user/user.module';\n\n@Module({\n  imports: [\n    EnvConfigModule,\n    HealthModule,\n    DbModule,\n    CacheModule,\n    ThrottlerModule.forRoot([{ ttl: 60000, limit: 60 }]),\n    AuthModule,\n    UserModule,\n    CompanyModule,\n    CompanyMemberModule,\n    SessionModule,\n  ],\n  controllers: [],\n  providers: [\n    { provide: APP_GUARD, useClass: AuthGuard },\n    { provide: APP_GUARD, useClass: RolesGuard },\n    { provide: APP_GUARD, useClass: FastifyThrottlerGuard },\n  ],\n})\nexport class AppModule {}\n```\n\nNote: DbModule and CacheModule are @Global() so they don't need to be imported by every module, but importing them in AppModule ensures they're initialized.\n\n### Step 3: Run Prettier\n```bash\nnpx prettier --write src/modules/auth/auth.module.ts src/modules/app/app.module.ts\n```\n\n### Step 4: Verify existing tests still pass\nRun: `npm run test:unit -- --testPathPatterns \"health|env-config\" 2>&1`\nExpected: existing tests should still pass (module changes shouldn't break isolated unit tests)\n\n### Step 5: Commit\n```bash\ngit add src/modules/auth/auth.module.ts src/modules/app/app.module.ts\ngit commit -m \"feat: assemble auth module with global guards and wire into app module\"\n```\n\nReport status: DONE, DONE_WITH_CONCERNS, NEEDS_CONTEXT, or BLOCKED"},"uuid":"c73f2888-d7ce-4483-b5bb-5927281b4025","timestamp":"2026-03-22T21:22:52.250Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/4thwithme/Documents/repo/no-name-proj/backend","sessionId":"3190ee6c-f60a-4a32-b4bf-dd77c9f97c0a","version":"2.1.81","gitBranch":"main","slug":"encapsulated-weaving-crystal"}
